---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-brand-950 border-t border-brand-800 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="text-brand-300 font-semibold text-lg">ZoningBase</p>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-1 max-w-md">
          Standardized US municipal zoning codes for commercial real estate professionals, developers, and architects.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm">
        <a href="/about/" class="text-text-muted hover:text-brand-200 transition-colors">About</a>
        <a href="/privacy/" class="text-text-muted hover:text-brand-200 transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms/" class="text-text-muted hover:text-brand-200 transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="text-text-muted hover:text-brand-200 transition-colors">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-brand-800 text-text-muted text-xs">
      <p>&copy; {year} ZoningBase. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="mt-1">Zoning data is sourced from public municipal records and may not reflect the most recent amendments. Always verify with local planning departments.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
